{"tid":431611,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[隔牆] Google Home Mini 被踢爆長期偷聽","createTime":"2017-10-11T01:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T07:04:35.000Z","uid":17103,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d31ca2ba7f67dc0b8635adbb43f8621df9740e2c","tid":431611,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:00:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2017/10/10/16456050/google-home-mini-always-recording-bug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F16456050%2Fgoogle-home-mini-always-recording-bug&d=cgLin8mi%2F3i1FLjXw5KkwMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7e04747d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2017/10/10/16456050/google-home-mini-always-recording-bug</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle&rsquo;s Home Mini needed a software patch to stop some of them from recording everything<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/YRP0sbfKskE8_AljJS5a-i99_9U=/0x0:2040x1360/920x613/filters:focal(857x517:1183x843):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/57091283/jbareham_170922_2006_0317.0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2FYRP0sbfKskE8_AljJS5a-i99_9U%3D%2F0x0%3A2040x1360%2F920x613%2Ffilters%3Afocal%28857x517%3A1183x843%29%3Aformat%28webp%29%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_image%2Fimage%2F57091283%2Fjbareham_170922_2006_0317.0.jpg&h=4800022a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle 智能喇叭出產至今最差的事, 由 Android Police 的 Artem Russakovskii 爆出.  他發現家中的 Google Home Mini 隨意地至幾乎全時間將他家中錄下一切聲音上載往 Google 的侍服器.  Google 已確定 Google Home Mini 機頂的 Touch Sensor 出現了故幛.<br />\n<br />\n所有智能喇叭設定當偵測到特定字詞如 Hey Google, Ok Google 後才開始錄音.  然後上載往 Google Server 再處理發回然後作出指令.  但 Google Home Mini  容許使用者將手指放在機頂作出相同錄音.  <br />\n<br />\n但 Artem 的 Google Home Mini 好像長時間感應到有手指在機頂然後錄音.  幸好當 Google Home Mini 錄音時會有顯示燈, 但並沒有其他聲音提示.  最後花了很多時間在歷史搜尋中找出了這事.  <br />\n<br />\nGoogle 的工程師努力不械下終於找出解決方法, 就是將該功能移除.  從此使用者必需用口令啟動錄音.<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 給 Android Police 的聲明:<br />\n<br />\n&quot; We have learned of an issue impacting a small number of Google Home Minis that could cause the touch mechanism to behave incorrectly. We are rolling out a software update today that should address the issue. If you're having any additional issues, please feel free to contact Google Support at 1-855-971-9121. &quot;<br />\n<br />\n小數產品故障聽起來是個好消息, 但這對 Google 的形象來說是一個衝擊.  因為很多人也擔心家中的智能喇叭在私下錄音和上載往其他地方.  最差的事就是令用家回想這些憂慮.  特別現在大家已經開始擔心到底 Google 已經收錄了多小私人對話.  <br />\n<br />\n最後, Google 連最簡單的表面物料下隱藏的按鍵也弄不好, 這令人對他的硬件生產也帶有懷疑.  當然大家也希望在正式十月十九日開賣前能把一切弄妥."},{"pid":"14bd56f9bf269d9b9f4419db1ccac5fab310c259","tid":431611,"uid":18292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73b0cfaceb7b03042fa6b18f11b2c67084452a9","tid":431611,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fa3e21892c99246a8fb48b397e3f5f55c57792","tid":431611,"uid":1552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:10:45.000Z","msg":"俾人踢爆左，咪話故障囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605c99cfea873049f34fbb2202f548b6e0c05fc8","tid":431611,"uid":2861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:15:44.000Z","msg":"Google 的工程師努力不械下終於找出解決方法, 就是將該功能移除<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debba0fa17841571962c7f1309f55eb6b396129f","tid":431611,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:19:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13f98aa8416faa6dc295744ee1f83ed74f25b4db","tid":431611,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:21:35.000Z","msg":"又係尼d假新聞"},{"pid":"7bd8049af4a16dd64e12830c15abfd04fc67d506","tid":431611,"uid":16904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:21:51.000Z","msg":"呢招勁<br />\n偷聽完可以話係壞制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f095f13546fe537eada14e457d298d853ddbcfe7","tid":431611,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f0f334604443c2a8d1192d6cdf51247cb7303e","tid":431611,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:37:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5af9862dc44e0c7f25a700ec4047e3aba1c9beed","tid":431611,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:24:37.000Z","msg":"落個PATCH 熄左盞錄音燈, 聽到HEY GOOGLE OK GOOGLE 先著返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa17afbcbf12773f2682bb8c781d95b5d4113a1","tid":431611,"uid":91685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:31:02.000Z","msg":"google不嬲毒過強國野<br />\n而家手機已經盡量減少用google d app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f44920a1c85532e54e2a454a28b17f8e862fa4","tid":431611,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T03:31:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Google 的工程師努力不械下終於找出解決方法, 就是將該功能移除<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebbaf243c96ecbe815b579e0797d441444705d6c","tid":431611,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T07:03:28.000Z","msg":